          <div class="callout-label">⚡ TL;DR — Pick by your bottleneck</div>
          <p><strong>Need more content shipped:</strong> theStacc ($99/mo) or Outrank ($49). <strong>Need on-page fixes auto-deployed:</strong> Search Atlas OTTO ($99) or Alli AI ($249). <strong>Need optimisation scoring while writing:</strong> Surfer SEO ($89). <strong>Want it all bundled with Local SEO + social:</strong> theStacc Bundle ($167/mo all-in).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want SEO running on autopilot — not another tool to learn?</h4>
            <p>theStacc handles content, on-page, Local SEO, and social on a schedule. <strong>$99/mo Content SEO · $167/mo Bundle</strong> — one dashboard, no tool stack.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
          </div>
        </div>

