          <li><strong>Test sites</strong> — 3 fresh domains: SaaS, local service, and ecom.</li>
          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — replicate a 6-article/mo agency package and a monthly on-page sweep.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — output shipped, indexing rate, ranking lift, time saved.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $2,340 across 10 platforms, Mar–May 2026.</li>
        </ul>

